Action settings

Ask clarifying question

When multiple actions seem to match what the customer wants, use this action in the clarifying question that lists possible options.

If you exclude the action and it has the highest confidence score, the action is triggered and no clarifying question is asked.

Learn more about asking a clarifying question

Change conversation topic
If a customer asks about a different topic, allow switching:
- Away to another action while progressing through this action
- Into this action if it matches the changed topic


Learn more about changing the conversation topic
